  <cateringDescription><![CDATA[<p>The Hotel is on a half board basis. </p>
<p>Each day a continental breakfast buffet with additional hot options is served within the on-site restaurant at Hotel Del Pui.</p>
<p>Evening meals are taken at the Hotel Magic which is a 50 metre walk from the hotel. </p>]]></cateringDescription>
  <deactivateThisPage>0</deactivateThisPage>
  <description><![CDATA[<p>Hotel Del Pui has a central location in the La Massana area of <a data-udi="umb://document/07c4ee80b2bd4b5c9640b262a5748dd7" href="/{localLink:umb://document/07c4ee80b2bd4b5c9640b262a5748dd7}" title="Arinsal">Arinsal</a>, just 50 metres from the Pa<span>l-Arinsal cable car, giving you easy access to the ski area. The hotel offers stylish accommodation with rustic décor and modern furnishings, it is a great choice for those looking for good value accommodation with a central location. </span></p>
<h2>Warm and welcoming </h2>
<p>With a variety of different occupancy rooms, this hotel is ideal for a single traveller, families and groups who want modern and simplistic accommodation in <a data-udi="umb://document/043e5aa9497c411db243e21ed0a5049b" href="/{localLink:umb://document/043e5aa9497c411db243e21ed0a5049b}" title="Andorra">Andorra</a>. The rooms have everything needed for a week in the mountains including Wi-Fi, a TV and most rooms have views across the resort and surrounding mountains. </p>
<h2>Great location</h2>
<p>Hotel Del Pui has a central location in the resort of La Massana, and is just a short walk to the Telecabina De La Massana, giving you access to the Vallnord ski resort with 60 kilometres of slopes - <span> ideal for families and beginners who are just learning. </span>The bus stop is 100 metres from the hotel giving you access to the other surrounding ski areas. If you want a day off from skiing, there is plenty to see and do including heading down to 'Andorra la Vella' to enjoy the (duty free) shopping centre, bowling or cinema and medieval churches. The <span>Caldea Thermal Complex is also a short bus ride away, and is a great option for the adults who want a break from skiing, boarding or winter walking - the adults only complex has a range of wellness areas including an indoor and outdoor thermal pool, a jacuzzi and saunas, perfect for an afternoon of pure relaxation.</span></p>
<p> </p>
<p> </p>
<p> </p>
<p> </p>]]></description>
